### Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

###

### Create a new book (Run this first to add ID 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Fellowship of the Ring",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "978-0261103573",
  "publishedYear": 1954
}

###

### Get a specific book by ID (Should return the book you just created)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

###

### Get a non-existent book by ID (Should return 404 Not Found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/999
